Source Code Repository
======================

The source code for this project is available at:
https://github.com/Eklipti/TelegramControlBot

This repository contains the complete source code required to build and
run the ControlBot application, including all dependencies and build
instructions.

For more information about this project, including installation
instructions and usage documentation, please refer to the README files
in the docs/ directory.

Third-Party Dependencies
========================

This project uses the following third-party libraries and frameworks:

- aiogram: Telegram Bot API framework for Python
- asyncio: Asynchronous I/O framework
- Standard Python libraries

Please refer to requirements.txt for the complete list of dependencies
and their versions.

